    "description": "1mg Capital India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Software Engineer for our Mysuru operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout 1mg Capital India:\n1mg Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 1mg Capital India!",
